      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've seen some biohacking forums saying that a massive loading dose for a short time is actually a standard way to correct a deficiency without needing blood tests first. if i only do it for like 10 days, isn't the risk of toxicity pretty much zero? i just want to get ahead of the winter slump before it gets worse.",
