      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already have some 50k IU softgels from a supplement i bought. if i take one every other day instead of every day, wouldn't that be way safer and still get me to that optimal level faster than just the tiny RDA amounts? it seems like a much more efficient way to do it since i'm already feeling the symptoms.",
